data.description: You will find this all brick home conveniently off the Fayetteville square and right around the corner from an elementary school. Containing 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, a designated living room and den, private office and separate dining room, this home has many sought after elements. A outdoor lover’s dream, this property has a 30ft above ground pool with a new pump last summer. There are also two large BBQ grills in the back yard along with a storage shed!
